text: Aigle Azur is an airline in France which operates flights within France but also to other European countries and some countries in Africa, for example Algeria. It's main base of operations is at Paris Orly Airport. The current Head, since 2008, is Méziane Idjerouidène. == Fleet == * 3x Airbus A319 * 3x Airbus A320 * 4x Airbus A321 ==References== Category:Airlines of France
